About Us

Alcheringa is the annual cultural festival of the Indian
Institute of Technology, Guwahati. A splendid idea realised
by a group of students in 1996 at IITG marked dawn of one of
Asia’s most exhilarating and significant cultural college fests
as we know it today.

About Us

Alcheringa is the annual cultural festival of the Indian Institute of Technology, Guwahati. A splendid idea realised by a group of students in 1996 at IITG marked dawn of one of Asia’s most exhilarating and significant cultural college fests as we know it today.
